transcripts: Stay cool in style this summer with Lasko hybrid fan. This 40 inch tower is not your average tower fan. The hybrid fan brings 30 percent more air delivery than standard tower fans providing maximum power in a sleek space saving design. The night light feature, remote control and wide spread isolation gives this unique fan functionally above the rest. Equipped with a fused safety plug, Lasko hybrid fan is the most polished way to stay cool all year around.
